  • Method Details

    • fromFile

      static ArangoConfigProperties fromFile()
      Reads properties from file arangodb.properties. Properties must be prefixed with @{code "arangodb"}, eg. @{code "arangodb.hosts=localhost:8529"}.

    • fromFile

      static ArangoConfigProperties fromFile(String fileName)
      Reads properties from file fileName. Properties must be prefixed with @{code "arangodb"}, eg. @{code "arangodb.hosts=localhost:8529"}.

    • fromFile

      static ArangoConfigProperties fromFile(String fileName, String prefix)
      Reads properties from file fileName. Properties must be prefixed with @{code prefix}, eg. @{code ".hosts=localhost:8529"}.

    • fromProperties

      static ArangoConfigProperties fromProperties(Properties properties)
      Creates ArangoConfigProperties from Java properties (Properties). Properties must be prefixed with @{code "arangodb"}, eg. @{code "arangodb.hosts=localhost:8529"}.

    • fromProperties

      static ArangoConfigProperties fromProperties(Properties properties, String prefix)
      Creates ArangoConfigProperties from Java properties (Properties). Properties must be prefixed with @{code prefix}, eg. @{code ".hosts=localhost:8529"}.
